<% provide :title, 'Help' %>
<div class="container font-weight-light my-5">  
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-2">
      Help<br />
      <div class="mt-1 small">
        <%= link_to 'How to download', '#how-to-download' %><br />
        <%= link_to 'Using an other broker', '#using-an-other-broker' %><br />
        <%= link_to 'What\'s the class', '#whats-the-class' %><br />
        <%= link_to 'An error occurred', '#an-error-occurred' %><br />
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-10">
      <h2>Help</h2>
      Do you necessary more help? You may be able to find solution.

      <a name="how-to-download">
        <h3 class="mt-5">How to download</h3>
      </a>
      <p class="text-justify">
        First, access to <%= link_to 'SBI SECURITIES Co.,Ltd.', 'https://site0.sbisec.co.jp/', target: :blank %>, input your name and password in each textboxes, click login button in Login page.
      </p>
      <div class="px-3 mb-5">
        <%= image_tag 'help/1.png', class: 'img-fluid img-thumbnail' %>
      </div>
      <p class="text-justify">
        Second, points on "口座管理" in top menu and click "トータルリターン".
      </p>
      <div class="px-3 mb-5">
        <%= image_tag 'help/2.png', class: 'img-fluid img-thumbnail' %>
      </div>
      <p class="text-justify">
        Third, click link of "保有中", "特定/一般" or "NISA/つみたてNISA".
      </p>
      <div class="px-3 mb-5">
        <%= image_tag 'help/3.png', class: 'img-fluid img-thumbnail' %>
      </div>
      <p class="text-justify">
        Last, click link of "CSVダウンロード", so has been downloaded CSV file.
      </p>
      <div class="px-3 mb-5">
        <%= image_tag 'help/4.png', class: 'img-fluid img-thumbnail' %>
      </div>

      <a name="using-an-other-broker">
        <h3 class="mt-5">Using an other broker</h3>
      </a>
      <p class="text-justify">
        If you using an other broker different from SBI SECURITIES Co.,Ltd., the following steps will help.
      </p>
      <p class="text-justify">
        Create a new CSV file, copy and past following text as header words.
        Input information of your investments after the second line.
        The file will be able to import in Organize.
        <div class="code rounded small">
          ファンド名,口座種別,評価金額,買付金額
        </div>
      </p>

